        <div id="WhatisBRICS">
          <h1>What is BRICS?</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
</div>
<div id="main text home page">
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='row'>
    <div id=whatisbricsbody>
      <div class='text-centre col-sm-9'>
      <p>BRICS: Brazil, Russia, India, China, and South Africa represent an
      association of five emerging national economies. All 5 members are leading
      or newly developed industrial nations. They represent half of world's population
      (3.6 billion people). The five nations have a combined nominal GDP of
      US$16.6 trillion, equivalent to approximately 22% of the gross world product.
      </p>
    </div>
    </div>
      <div class='text-centre col-sm-3'>
